{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- Please place categories where indicated at the bottom of this page and interwikis at Wikidata (see [[Wikipedia:Wikidata]]) -->
{{High risk}}
==Usage==
{{Warning|'''This template should ''not'' be used in articles or in ongoing disputes.'''<br/>It is intended solely for genuine housekeeping purposes and should not be used to prematurely conclude discussions or proposals unless all participants agree to do so.}}
===Basics===
* To include a [[Wikipedia:Shortcut|shortcut]], pass a [[Help:Template#Parameters|parameter]]: {{Tnull|Historical|2=WP:SHORT}}.
* To provide a last-updated date, use the named parameter {{para|last}} or {{para|date}}, i.e. {{Tnull|Historical|2=last=1 January 2000}}. This should only be used for {{em|substantive}} updates, not things like bot tweaks or typo fixes.
* To provide a briefer form of the text, use {{Tnull|Historical|2=brief=yes}}
* Specifying the {{para|type}} parameter:
** For a former [[Wikipedia:Policy|policy]], use {{para|type|policy}}
** For a former [[Wikipedia:Guideline|guideline]], use {{para|type|guideline}}
** For a page closed down by explicit community [[Wikipedia:Consensus|consensus]], use {{para|type|woundup}}
** For a former [[Wikipedia:Essays|essay]] which at one time had consensus, but is no longer relevant use {{para|type|essay}}
* To append the text of the template, and provide an [[Wikipedia:COMMENT|explanatory comment]], use {{Tnull|Historical|2=comment=explanatory text here}}.  Aliases for {{para|comment}} are {{para|reason}} and {{para|result}}.
** If you want to point to a successor page, use {{tlx|Superseded}} instead of {{tnull|Historical}}.
* Pages using this template will be placed into [[:Category:Inactive project pages]] unless the parameter {{para|category|no}} is given: {{tnull|Historical|2=category=no}} (user and user talk pages are not categorized).
* For related [[:Category:Wikipedia header templates|Wikipedia header templates]], see [[Wikipedia:Template messages/Wikipedia namespace|Template messages/Wikipedia namespace]].
* Please note that this template is {{em|not}} appropriate for [[WP:PORTAL|portals]], which exist for the purpose of informing readers on a given topic and, as such, can never truly be "inactive".
*It is also not appropriate for inactive WikiProjects or task forces, which are dealt with according to the [[Wikipedia:WikiProject Council/Guide#Dealing with inactive WikiProjects|WikiProject Council/Guide]]; these should be tagged with {{tlx|WikiProject status|Defunct}} or {{tlx|WikiProject status|Inactive}}.
*To remove the message {{dc|Either the page is no longer relevant or consensus on its purpose has become unclear. To revive discussion, seek broader input via a forum such as the [[Wikipedia:Village pump (proposals)|village pump]].}} then set {{para|brief|y}}.

===Adding shortcuts===
*In addition, a shortcut can be added to this template by using the following syntax:

:{{Tlc|Historical|SHORTCUT}}

*Up to 5 shortcuts can be added to this template in this fashion:

:{{Tlc|Historical|SHORTCUT1|SHORTCUT2|SHORTCUT3|SHORTCUT4|SHORTCUT5}}

===TemplateData===
<templatedata>
{
	"params": {
		"1": {
			"label": "Shortcut 1",
			"type": "wiki-page-name",
			"description": "Shortcut",
			"example": "WP:FOO"
		},
		"2": {
			"label": "Shortcut 2",
			"type": "wiki-page-name"
		},
		"3": {
			"label": "Shortcut 3",
			"type": "wiki-page-name"
		},
		"4": {
			"label": "Shortcut 4",
			"type": "wiki-page-name"
		},
		"5": {
			"label": "Shortcut 5",
			"type": "wiki-page-name"
		},
		"last": {
			"description": "The date of the last substantative update to this page.",
			"type": "date",
			"suggested": true,
			"label": "Last update",
			"example": "1 January 2001",
			"aliases": [
				"date"
			]
		},
		"type": {
			"type": "line",
			"suggested": true,
			"description": "The type of page it refers to. Recognized values: policy, guideline, woundup, dbr, section, essay. Optional, by default will output a generic statement.",
			"example": "policy",
			"label": "Type of page",
			"suggestedvalues": [
				"policy",
				"guideline",
				"woundup",
				"dbr",
				"section",
				"essay"
			]
		},
		"brief": {
			"type": "boolean",
			"description": "Whether to use a shortened message.",
			"default": "no",
			"label": "Brief message?",
			"example": "yes"
		},
		"comment": {
			"type": "string",
			"suggested": true,
			"description": "A message explaining why the page is obsolete",
			"aliases": [
				"reason",
				"result"
			],
			"label": "Comment or reason"
		},
		"category": {
			"description": "Whether to include this in [[Category:Inactive project pages]]",
			"example": "no",
			"type": "boolean",
			"default": "yes",
			"label": "Categorize?"
		}
	},
	"paramOrder": [
		"1",
		"2",
		"3",
		"4",
		"5",
		"last",
		"type",
		"brief",
		"comment",
		"category"
	],
	"format": "inline",
	"description": "Mark a page as currently inactive and is retained for historical reference."
}
</templatedata>

==See also==
* {{tl|WikiProject status}}
* {{tl|failed}} for proposals that were never adopted
* [[Wikipedia:Template messages/Wikipedia namespace]] for a listing of Wikipedia namespace banners.

